OL,4,Cgrassroots football from next season
OL,6,FSin bins will be introduced in Welsh
OL,7,Fgrassroots from next season, it has
OL,8,Fbeen announced.
OL,10,FThe new rules will apply to both the
OL,11,Fsenior and youth games later this year
OL,12,Ffollowing a unanimous decision by the
OL,13,FFootball Association of Wales' (FAW)
OL,14,FCommunity Game Board.
OL,16,FSin bins - formally called Temporary
OL,17,FDismissals - will only apply to
OL,18,Foffences involving dissent, with
OL,19,Fplayers set to be shown a yellow card
OL,20,Fwhich will see them leave the pitch
OL,21,Ffor a minimum of 10 minutes.
