OL,6,FThe clamp down on dissent follows
OL,7,Ftrials in six grassroots competitions
OL,8,Fthis season, which saw offences
OL,9,Freduced by slightly more than a third.
OL,11,FRed cards for offensive, insulting or
OL,12,Fabusive language also reduced by 32%,
OL,13,Faccording to the .
OL,15,FThe tighter regulations will not be
OL,16,Fintroduced in junior grassroots
OL,17,Ffootball, although trials will be
OL,18,Fcarried out to see whether the change
OL,19,Fshould be made there too.
