OL,4,Cgrassroots football from next season
OL,6,FFAW CEO Noel Mooney said: "Introducing
OL,7,FTemporary Dismissals is a significant
OL,8,Fstep on our journey to making football
OL,9,Fthe most inclusive, accessible and
OL,10,Fsuccessful sport in Cymru. That means
OL,11,Fcreating safe and enjoyable
OL,12,Fenvironments for all participants in
OL,13,Ffootball, including match officials."
OL,15,FMark Adams, chairman of the FAW
OL,16,FCommunity Game Board, said it aims to
OL,17,Freduce "dissent and abuse towards
OL,18,Fmatch officials," with Welsh
OL,19,Fgrassroots football growing "at an
OL,20,Fincredible rate."
